OL,3,CTop KGB defector Oleg Gordievsky dies
OL,4,Caged 86
OL,6,FTop KGB defector Oleg Gordievsky has
OL,7,Fdied at the age of 86.
OL,9,FCode-named Hetman, Mr Gordievsky was
OL,10,Fone of the most important spies of the
OL,11,FCold War.
OL,13,FSurrey Police said officers were
OL,14,Fcalled to an address in Godalming on 4
OL,15,FMarch, where "an 86-year-old man was
OL,16,Ffound dead at the property".
