OL,6,FIt said counterterrorism officers are
OL,7,Fleading the investigation, but "the
OL,8,Fdeath is not currently being treated
OL,9,Fas suspicious" and "there is nothing
OL,10,Fto suggest any increased risk to
OL,11,Fmembers of the public".
OL,13,FFor more than a decade Mr Gordievsky's
OL,14,Freports gave Britain invaluable
OL,15,Finsights into the thinking of the
OL,16,FSoviet leadership and the covert
OL,17,Fmachinations of the KGB.
