OL,4,Caged 86
OL,6,FA man walking past him in the street
OL,7,Fin Moscow carrying a Harrods bag and
OL,8,Feating a Mars bar was the sign that
OL,9,Fhis message had been received and the
OL,10,Frescue was under way.
OL,12,FOn August 2 1985, in a daring
OL,13,Foperation personally approved by prime
OL,14,Fminister Margaret Thatcher, two MI6
OL,15,Fofficers, Raymond Asquith, great-
OL,16,Fgrandson of former Liberal prime
OL,17,Fminister Herbert Asquith, and Andrew
OL,18,FGibbs, managed to give the Soviet
OL,19,Fsurveillance the slip and smuggle
OL,20,Ftheir man across the border into
OL,21,FFinland hidden in the boot of a car.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
