OL,6,FIn his absence, Mr Gordievsky was
OL,7,Fsentenced to death in Russia for
OL,8,Ftreason.
OL,10,FMeanwhile, he established a new life,
OL,11,Fliving in a safe house in London,
OL,12,Fwriting a number of books and being
OL,13,Freceived by Mrs Thatcher in Chequers
OL,14,Fand Mr Reagan in the Oval Office.
OL,16,FIn 2007, the former KGB officer was
OL,17,Fhonoured by Queen Elizabeth II, being
OL,18,Fmade a Companion of the Order of Saint
OL,19,FMichael and St George (CMG) in a
OL,20,Fceremony at Buckingham Palace.
